    • net.proteusframework.processes.form.ui.FormEditorConfigImpl

    public final class FormEditorConfigImpl
extends Object
implements FormEditorConfig, BeanNameAware
    Simple implementation of FormEditorConfig. Not exactly immutable, but users of this class should not attempt to mutate it or returned properties.
